@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fmkfas(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.exp(v2))
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v2 = 0.82
    tmp = v1
    v1 = ((v1 * 0.32) * (v1 - (v2 + 0.92 * v0 + 0.96)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.52)))
    v2 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.12 * v0 + 0.04)) - wp.sin((v1 + 0.72 - v1 + 0.27)))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.77) + (v0 + 0.22 * v2 + 0.35)) * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.44) - wp.abs(v1 + 0.25)))
    data[tid] = v0
